route replace table main default via 192.0.2.1 dev mgmt0 metric 200
route replace table mgmt default via 192.0.2.1 dev mgmt0 src 192.0.2.10 metric 200
rule replace priority 100 from 192.0.2.10/32 lookup mgmt
route replace table main default via 198.51.100.1 dev app0 metric 50
route replace table app default via 198.51.100.1 dev app0 src 198.51.100.10 metric 50
rule replace priority 110 from 198.51.100.10/32 lookup app
